Invocation Name: new york guide
des: This New York City guide skill provides helpful travel information to NYC visitors and residents alike. You can ask for top attractions as well as suggestions for things to do in New York City. You can also ask for local NYC news to assist in planning a fun trip.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
